1. *Čekate* li vi na nekoga? (Are you *waiting* for someone?)
2. Ne *čekate* dovoljno dugo. (You're not *waiting* long enough.)
3. *Čekate* me već pola sata. (You've been *waiting* for me for half an hour.)
4. Oni neće *čekati* predugo. (They won't *wait* for too long.)
5. Ja ne mogu *čekati* celi dan. (I can't *wait* all day.)
6. *Čekate* li da vam pomognem? (Are you *waiting* for me to help you?)
7. Moramo *čekati* još malo. (We have to *wait* a little longer.)
8. Ne želim *čekati* više. (I don't want to *wait* anymore.)
9. *Čekajući* te, dosađivao sam se. (While *waiting* for you, I was bored.)
10. Mogli bismo *čekati* ovde. (We could *wait* here.)